df = pd.read_csv('inventario.csv', sep = ';')
writer = pd.ExcelWriter('inventario_por_bodega.xlsx', engine='xlsxwriter')

for idx in df.iloc[:, 2].unique():

    df_idx.to_excel(writer, sheet_name=str(idx))
    
writer.close()
